OOC: Oh wait, yes you have. Sorry.

Vulois turned around, seeing them attack. His anger bubbled up. He 
was under a lot of stress because his mission was falling apart.

"I DON'T NEED THIS RIGHT NOW!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!"

Vulois ran infront of the rest and just gazed at all the attackers. 
Some of his past Predacon personality was taking affect now. He just 
thought of them all as just somemore victims(Tazz rules!). He 
gathered up Matrix energy and just simply released it in a giant 
blast from his pond.

"DIE, YOU ANGER FILLED SCUM!"
